{"tid":916276,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"新晉女導演　拍「野」響朵 盼港府視填海為最後選項","createTime":"2018-11-25T15:07:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-28T02:18:12.000Z","uid":25558,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"bb1237b6ba13b03ee4a6de567f2b371eb33e2525","tid":916276,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T15:07:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181125/20554006\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181125%2F20554006&d=KuT%2Ftr4FTowZ5QrYLSFrBVKzBYqMCiHg3GgvTcrvEuQ%3D&h=c8bc2e7f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181125%2F20554006&h=6a99e35b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181125/20554006</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年11月25日 <br />\n<br />\n新晉女導演　拍「野」響朵<br />\n盼港府視填海為最後選項<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181125/large/25la7p1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181125%2Flarge%2F25la7p1.jpg&h=9cc238cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n生態攝影師黃遂心為捕捉米埔候鳥最精采畫面，趴在泥地守候半小時。許頌明攝 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【醉心大自然】<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】22歲的黃遂心（Daphne）趴在泥地，手持長鏡頭匐匍前行，逐吋接近漁塘覓食的候鳥，半小時守候換來10多秒精采影像。她是新晉紀錄片導演，剛完成大學畢業作品《白海豚失樂園》，用影像紀錄中華白海豚生存困境，例如被觀光小艇追逐包圍，在飄滿垃圾海面穿梭等。作品入圍今年奧地利Innsbruck Nature Film Festival電影節最佳年青導演組別。<br />\n<br />\n記者：潘柏林<br />\n<br />\n採訪當日，黃遂心在塱原拍攝雀鳥，背負10多公斤的器材仍然步履輕盈，「啲裝備咁重，你日出夜出就會慣」。她自小醉心自然，在家看英國廣播公司（BBC）的生態紀錄片，放假隨父母去郊野公園觀鳥賞蟲，生日禮物收到儍瓜機便匆匆趕去米埔拍攝黑臉琵鷺，「影到一點已經覺得好開心。」中五那年因為考試表現好，爸爸獎勵一部單鏡反光機，自此開始生態攝影。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181125/large/25la7p4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181125%2Flarge%2F25la7p4.jpg&h=d42236a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黃遂心背負10多公斤的器材仍然步履輕盈。許頌明攝  <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181125/large/a0701a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181125%2Flarge%2Fa0701a.jpg&h=f7a244c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黃遂心大學畢業作《白海豚失樂園》紀錄中華白海豚的生存困境。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181125/large/a0701b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181125%2Flarge%2Fa0701b.jpg&h=792d432a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n紀錄片記述大小船隻駛經白海豚棲息水域。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n《白海豚失樂園》入圍奧地利影展<br />\n<br />\n中學畢業後，她升讀英國法爾茅斯大學（Falmouth University），主修「海洋與自然歷史攝影」，大學二年級一邊學習拍攝紀錄片，一邊做兩份兼職賺錢買器材。第一套作品《Let it Bee: Keeper of British Black Bees》，講述養蜂人用自然方式飼養英國黑蜂，結果這份大學功課大獲好評，老師更建議參加不同電影節，成功入圍6個影展。<br />\n<br />\n第二套紀錄片是大學畢業作品，她憶述當時同學構思在外國拍攝，自己決定返回香港拍攝中華白海豚，「佢係香港20年前回歸吉祥動物，但20年之間個命運唔係好吉祥，20年間（數量）跌咗75%，由188條跌到落47條」。<br />\n<br />\n黃遂心前後用30多日跟隨海豚監測人員出海，只有3日拍攝到中華白海豚蹤迹，目睹海豚面臨越來越多威脅，「呢度起緊三跑、呢度起緊大橋，海面又好多垃圾」。她慨嘆，很多海豚傷痕纍纍，最常見背鰭受傷腐爛，海豚要在垃圾中浮潛，更被大澳觀豚船追趕。<br />\n<br />\n《白海豚失樂園》入圍今年奧地利Innsbruck Nature Film Festival電影節最佳年青導演組別。黃遂心指，在外國播放作品，觀眾詫異香港有粉紅色中華白海豚棲息，「香港咁幸運可以擁有，佢哋會覺得好詫異香港點解唔去保育，而繼續去損害佢哋生境地」。<br />\n<br />\n她希望更多人明白海豚面對困境，又呼籲港府將填海視為最後選項，「人類唔可以自以為高高在上就可以破壞其他物種嘅生態，因為我哋共存喺一個世界裏面。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n盼畢業後入BBC紀錄生態<br />\n<br />\n黃遂心希望畢業後在BBC自然歷史部工作，繼續拍攝野生生態。《白海豚失樂園》周二（27日）晚上在中大免費放映，市民可網上報名，名額有限。<br />\n<br />\n報名網址： <a href=\"https://cloud.itsc.cuhk.edu.hk/mycuform/view.php?id=225857\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloud.itsc.cuhk.edu.hk%2Fmycuform%2Fview.php%3Fid%3D225857&d=KuT%2Ftr4FTowZ5QrYLSFrBVKzBYqMCiHg3GgvTcrvEuQ%3D&h=830b834a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://cloud.itsc.cuhk.edu.hk/mycuform/view.php?id=225857</a>  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n鍾國斌︰紡織界8月曾訪美游說<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n昨晚六合彩開獎結果"},{"pid":"e845ba3eae594fac1e540153ce1cb0da3300ff9d","tid":916276,"uid":71341,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T18:59:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f6ff010072843499c86fb3ed7133f94bd3b5b9f7","tid":916276,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T10:23:06.000Z","msg":"人地正經POST你都搞<br />\n你D咁嘅SONY死龍友返去影女影裸體啦<br />\n<br />\n死五毛"},{"pid":"859eabe0b9338711e61f0baff1c8b419a3dbc89d","tid":916276,"uid":38218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T15:57:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://vimeo.com/250231923\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvimeo.com%2F250231923&d=KuT%2Ftr4FTowZ5QrYLSFrBVKzBYqMCiHg3GgvTcrvEuQ%3D&h=731b291b\" target=\"_blank\">https://vimeo.com/250231923</a>"},{"pid":"4d066330d9c5ce720edb4e8fc8c2d86b7587032e","tid":916276,"uid":38218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T16:01:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://vimeo.com/daphnewong\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvimeo.com%2Fdaphnewong&d=KuT%2Ftr4FTowZ5QrYLSFrBVKzBYqMCiHg3GgvTcrvEuQ%3D&h=ba16658a\" target=\"_blank\">https://vimeo.com/daphnewong</a><br />\n佢嘅片主要upload 係 Vimeo<br />\nPersonal website: <a href=\"https://www.daphnewong.org/#home\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.daphnewong.org%2F%23home&d=KuT%2Ftr4FTowZ5QrYLSFrBVKzBYqMCiHg3GgvTcrvEuQ%3D&h=fedc31db\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.daphnewong.org/#home</a> <br />\nig: <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/daphnewongphoto/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fdaphnewongphoto%2F&d=KuT%2Ftr4FTowZ5QrYLSFrBVKzBYqMCiHg3GgvTcrvEuQ%3D&h=f929aa3d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/daphnewongphoto/</a>"},{"pid":"7b42b0b8466a27ce27437b61bca85841a8d1b4d2","tid":916276,"uid":83648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T16:08:01.000Z","msg":"已經唔記得吉祥物係白海豚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pi